Revision history for Perl extension DBIx::PasswordIniFile

1.1  2005-Apr-17
     - First version, too many bugs

2.00 2011-Jan-04

    - Changed content model of .ini file. This release does not assume any 
      specific DSN format. Maintained compatibility with previous version
      
    - Deprecated functions that subclass DBI
      
    - Changed default cipher algorith to Crypt::Blowfish instead of 
      Crypt::Blowfish_PP
      
    - More tests

